## Working in this repo

- **TASKS.md is the current work list.** If it exists, treat the topmost unchecked item as the active task. Update checkbox state (`[ ]` pending → `[~]` in progress → `[x]` done) as work progresses.
- **GOTCHAS.md lists hard-won pitfalls.** Before writing code in any area where a gotcha exists, follow its prescribed fix. Run `/gotcha` to add or review entries.
- **`.claude/project.json` configures toolkit commands** (test runners, log-audit command, eval runner, etc.). Every key is optional; skills skip gracefully when a key is missing.

